Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.12,0:00:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 信乃也好 莊介也好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.29,0:00:07.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都這麼晚了也不聯繫一下 幹什麼去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.20,0:00:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心的話讓五狐去找找看怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.19,0:00:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 我又沒在擔心他們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.61,0:00:17.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了 濱路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.22,0:00:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天要不要去學校參觀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.07,0:00:23.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學校？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.72,0:00:28.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正小信和莊介也會暫時滯留一段時間的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.61,0:00:31.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話 對你來說學校就是必要的了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.28,0:00:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.87,0:00:39.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.56,0:00:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.87,0:00:53.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.75,0:00:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的 傷口並不是很深
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.33,0:01:01.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨 快去通知里見
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.65,0:01:02.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.27,0:01:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再動了 莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.28,0:01:06.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.78,0:01:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 沒想到這個傢伙會派上用場呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.63,0:01:14.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎 怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.85,0:01:16.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它放進你外套的口袋裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.20,0:01:18.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自放進來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.84,0:01:22.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.23,0:01:25.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概 是那位鬼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.46,0:01:26.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.56,0:01:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.02,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:35.02,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:38.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.02,0:01:38.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:42.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.42,0:01:42.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.80,0:01:49.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:55.67,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.20,0:01:55.67,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.08,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.67,0:01:59.08,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.65,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:01.65,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:05.15,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:05.15,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:10.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.15,0:02:10.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.89,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.12,0:02:14.89,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:19.20,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.89,0:02:19.20,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.27,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:24.27,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.47,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.27,0:02:26.47,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.94,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.47,0:02:28.94,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:32.68,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.94,0:02:32.68,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.51,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.68,0:02:36.51,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.78,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.51,0:02:38.78,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.42,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:42.42,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:47.09,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.42,0:02:47.09,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:51.73,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.09,0:02:51.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.73,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:54.73,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.32,0:03:03.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不能讓那鬼和孩子逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.46,0:03:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要把他們找出來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.20,0:03:09.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 也不要忘了那把刀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.41,0:03:14.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是傳說中的妖刀——村雨
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:16.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會在那種小鬼手上
